nodes.documentation:
@title Rates
@dev Rates contract
 * Stores the rates between a reference token and other tokens
 * @author Cyril Lapinte - <cyril.lapinte@mtpelerin.com>
 * Error messages
E01: Address of the reference token must be defined
E02: Cannot update more rates than tokens
E03: Cannot update more inverted rates than tokens
E04: Token Id does not exists
E05: Token address is not defined
E06: Cannot add more rates than tokens
E07: Cannot add more inverted rates than tokens
nodes.name: Rates

nodes.documentation: @dev Constructor
@dev Update many rates
nodes.name: updateManyRates

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the reference token used to define the token rate against
nodes.name: referenceToken

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the number of digits after the decimal point for rate and invertedRate values
nodes.name: ratePrecision

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the list of tokens inside the contract
nodes.name: tokens

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the rate for a token respectfully to the reference token
nodes.name: rate

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the inverted rate for a token respectfully to the reference token
nodes.name: invertedRate

nodes.documentation: @dev Return the last time the rate was updated for a token
nodes.name: updatedAt

nodes.documentation: @dev Update a rate
nodes.name: updateRate

nodes.name: addManyTokens
